'''Borno''' in gelle i woyla maso hunanci hautugo [[Naajeeriya|Najeriya]]. Iwodi mangu leddi jaradun kamannin kilomita 57,799km den kuma i duduki yibbe jarabe adadadi yebbe 5,925,668 i kirkirak yebbe kidayar leddi di lebbi 2006 maude. Gelle Leddi inhankoke i [[Maiduguri]]. [[Babagana Umara Zulum]] inhankoke ardido leddi tun gada zabe mako no inwodi lebbi 2019 har zuwa ma itaikijo mako gwamnajo’un kuma inhankoke [[Usman Mamman Durkwa]]. [[Diiwal Borno]] yodegodi iyaka den leddi tati i [[Adamawa| Diiwal Adamawa]] dekkuma i fobbi na [[Diiwal Gombe]] dekkuma fobbina daga hirna dekkuma i [[Diiwal Yobe]] daga hirna sannan daga dunwadu iyaka lesdi [[Niger]], [[Kamerun|Kamaru]], dekkuma i [[Caadi|Chadi]]. <ref>https://www.britannica.com/place/Bornu-historical-kingdom-and-emirate-Nigeria</ref> <ref>https://www.hurstpublishers.com/book/history-borno/</ref>



